    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean, you're saying they \"often backfire,\" but isn't it true that for certain industries, like steel or tech, it's basically the only way to keep them from being wiped out by overseas competition? seems like a necessary trade-off to keep the country self-sufficient.",
